Repeat: on the next stitch (the center ofhe slipped group) insert right-hand needle down through the 5 loose strands, bring needle up and transfer the 5 strands to left-hand needle, purl the 5 strands and the next stitch together as one stitch; p9
End Row: on the next stitch (the center ofhe slipped group) insert right-hand needle down through the 5 loose strands, bring needle up and transfer the 5 strands to left-hand needle, purl the 5 strands and the next stitch together as one stitch; p4

Repeat: insert needle down through the 5 loose strands, bring them up and purl them with next stitch as before; p9
